THIS VERSION IS OBSOLETE. AREA13 IS DEAD, TREEROAD IS GOING TO BE REWRITTEN USING PYLONS (MAYBE)
TreeRoad-Area13 demo available here : http://jackfuncoco.pistaches.net/treeroad-demo/

TreeRoad is a Django-based manager for rrdfiles. It can parse the collectd arborescence and initiate graph jobs.
https://github.com/pstch/treeroad
